text: Marija Vuković (; born 25 March 1990) is a Serbian footballer who plays as a forward and has appeared for the Serbia women's national team. ==Career== Vuković has been capped for the Serbia national team, appearing for the team during the 2019 FIFA Women's World Cup qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1990 births Category:Living people Category:Serbian women's footballers Category:Serbia women's international footballers Category:Women's association football forwards Category:Serbian expatriate footballers Category:Serbian expatriate sportspeople in Russia Category:Expatriate women's footballers in Russia Category:Ryazan-VDV players
title: Marija Vuković (footballer)
